author: Fextralife
description:
Nightreign Classes Ranked - Which Nightfarers Are The Best For You? Classes Tier List
In this Elden Ring Nightreign video, we're going to be taking a look at all eight classes in the game. I'm going to be ranking them all. I'm going to be telling you about each one of them, why you may want to play it, or why you might not. I'll also be talking about why we've ranked them the way that we've ranked them, so you can get a better understanding of what you can expect from the different characters in the game.

Elden Ring Nightreign Wiki: https://eldenringnightreign.wiki.fextralife.com/Elden+Ring+Nightreign+Wiki

Blades of Fire BEHIND THE SCENES - Director Interview

https://store.playstation.com/concept/10011854/
Sponsored by:  MercurySteam & 505 Games

In this Fextralife video, We're going to be going behind the scenes with the creative director and CEO of Mercury Steam Enric Alvarez, and we're gonna be talking about how Blades of Fire came to be, what it's inspiration was, and what some of the design choices in the game were inspired by.  If you’re want to hear his thoughts about the worlds of Blades of fire, then this is the interview you won’t want to miss.
